Node.DataCrLf:
copy database from old to new optinally switching from old to new when new achieves the same state as old.
Algorithm: dirty file copy then passes using incremental backup bitmap and updated blocks copy from old to new.
During last past system switch 10 is on and global access from other processes is disabled.
It is downtime of application.
If OnLineSwitch=1 then db switch also under system switch 10 set
After database switch from old to new completed system switch 10 is cleared
